
Breadth First Search (BFS)

Compile:

    make            # Baseline CDP version
    make all        # All versions
    make test       # Test compiled versions
    make test-all   # Compile all versions and test them

Run:

    ./bfs.<version>
    ./bfs.<version> -h  # Help

Source: A. Danalis, G. Marin, C. McCurdy, J. S. Meredith, P. C. Roth, K. Spafford, V. Tipparaju, and J. S. Vetter. "The Scalable Heterogeneous Computing (SHOC) Benchmark Suite." In Proceedings of the 3rd Workshop on General-Purpose Computation on Graphics Processing Units, GPGPU3, pp. 63â€“74, ACM, 2010.

